name: Discover dataset
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nrouyer/assemblylineplanning/refs/heads/main/dataset/rotorcraft_assemblyline_20tasks.csv" AS row
RETURN row LIMIT 5

name: GDS DAG algorithms
query:
CALL gds.list() 
YIELD name, description, signature
WHERE toLower(name) CONTAINS "gds.dag"
RETURN name, description, signature

name: Set constraints
Load Workstation nodes
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nrouyer/assemblylineplanning/refs/heads/main/dataset/rotorcraft_assemblyline_20tasks.csv" AS row
MERGE (w:Workstation {id: row.Workstation})
WITH DISTINCT w
RETURN count(w) AS nbWorkstations;

name: Load Team nodes
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nrouyer/assemblylineplanning/refs/heads/main/dataset/rotorcraft_assemblyline_20tasks.csv" AS row
MERGE (t:Team {id: row.Team})
WITH distinct t
RETURN count(t) AS nbTeams;

name: Load Rotorcraft nodes
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nrouyer/assemblylineplanning/refs/heads/main/dataset/rotorcraft_assemblyline_20tasks.csv" AS row
WITH row WHERE row.`Helicopter Model` STARTS WITH 'Model'
MERGE (r:Rotorcraft {id: row.`Helicopter Model`})
WITH distinct r
RETURN count(r);

name: Load Task nodes
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nrouyer/assemblylineplanning/refs/heads/main/dataset/rotorcraft_assemblyline_20tasks.csv" AS row
WITH row, 
{
  granularity: row.Granularity, 
  estimatedDurationHours: toInteger(row.`Estimated Duration (hrs)`),
  realDurationHours: toInteger(row.`Real Duration (hrs)`)
} AS props
MERGE (t:Task {id: row.`Task ID`})
  ON CREATE SET t += props
  ON MATCH SET t += props
RETURN count(t) AS nbTasks;
